::Bazooka::

    Bazooka travels down twisting corodors to find Megatron. He knows he must 
get an assignment. Bazooka is out of place he belongs on the outside, not in 
here, but his primary programing to get a mission will not let him leave.
    "Bazooka Terrorize" He mutters to himself. He likes his Beast mode, he 
decides to test out his Robot mode for a little while. Looking himself over 
he can see his Beast mode head on his arm and on the other an axe/gun. "This 
is good"
    Walking around he gets lost many times, but find just the right corodor 
to put him back on track. "The bot known as Shredder has helped much." He 
thinks to himslef.
    Bazooka belives he is nearing Megatron. But before he does he runs into 
another Transformer.
